198315273129.value: Open source JSON-based database library, packaged with NPM. Useful for smaller projects where you don't want to go through the trouble of implementing a more scalable database solution. You can install it with 'npm i databased'.

1702369440566.value: A basic business website for one of my friends who provides janitorial services. Only two pages complete because they haven't been focusing on their business much recently.
